{"tid":108831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被人迫去髮廊仲慘過上刑場","createTime":"2017-02-05T14:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T02:51:19.000Z","uid":71008,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b738284d8b8a5d97d8380b64f8c3af70ca0dfd46","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"今日我老母話我頭髮太長，要剪。我一向都係俾老豆剪頭髮嘅，咁我就問佢放左工可唔可以幫我剪。點知佢話:&quot;你老母都唔知係唔係生左個智障仔，廿幾歲都淨係敢俾屋企人剪頭髮，我話俾你知今日唔係對面街間髮廊剪就咪撚駛番嚟打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot; 跟住就嗌我&quot;死出去&quot;(好大聲，所以我好合作)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到髮廊，我即刻覺得自己墮入咗無間地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，見到一班頭髮五顏六色嘅潮女型男係到傾計。收銀個mk仔(好似忍住笑):&quot;先生剪髮啊?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我話係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住就帶左我去洗頭。去到個位我先法國居然係個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白頭mk妹幫我洗頭，我個心即刻沉左一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個mk妹對手掂我個下我即刻好似觸左電咁，開始好緊張。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我成個身即刻硬曬，個mk妹都feel到，開始忍唔住笑。我聽到d笑聲仲加驚，大聲喘氣，搞到佢大聲笑咗出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我去到e到已經忍唔到，唔理個mk妹企番起身走左去收銀到俾錢。個mk仔話:&quot;先生你頭都未洗完㖞&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔理佢，擺低錢跑左出去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc40e336be4c01abc18984991991de8003b79465","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2544b98ecf7847d948ee4ef18479e44bca190b97","tid":108831,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"潮文"},{"pid":"6a38fce4060d4e5e1dc276efbb52ecce7adb34f6","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潮文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真咖"},{"pid":"df0571f80eb1f6217e5c77e889fedee14a3e8987","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cf7d22e81dfd910e7234d27b50507ca19dd19a","tid":108831,"uid":81262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc4154c736a482bdafbf83dfc853d01279596bd","tid":108831,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:47:03.000Z","msg":"你老豆用心良苦,想你去完髮廊剪髮就行上兩層叫雞破處咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fe131c6982cd51977e2153d3eb30069348914b","tid":108831,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"ba337593c71d4aa21419aaf7c73ab841828868ef","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141fa95c30775ad4b0e948bfda6940b605b19e2e","tid":108831,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22e576ea4e822251a71a884f32b1a007446fb25","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你見到我真人唔會咁諗"},{"pid":"767bc6f755ad00362a7724a322ba22f752e7512a","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06243b66f96523d0de86573cff9ba397fdca575f","tid":108831,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"你老豆可能過左身"},{"pid":"e3c272f5ab624cd0d70fd37a03e856a4ea7c629a","tid":108831,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"之後呢"},{"pid":"d654defc540c7576db4cae725d9bc51d4e9b749f","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆可能過左身</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母同我求情，話唔好咁樣迫個仔，老豆同佢嗌左一陣交先俾我入番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話&quot;你條廢柴就成世攬住你老母啦&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都覺得我好冇用"},{"pid":"9e703c24ba7dcb0886bcc30935351e624c845e1d","tid":108831,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"死假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bc60d414becede5c3626ebef07f3ed5d35a44b","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解咁講"},{"pid":"8c64f5b345b3890d967f7f7ff9217324d8e6bdd9","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687a8f3b20215927f1cf017532b72996d8a0fb35","tid":108831,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:51:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，無人回你d垃圾post架啦"},{"pid":"b7191b0c1870f49b55c61b5318eee4523ed142e0","tid":108831,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"i know..."},{"pid":"c504e98c242b1676d60baf316ed9a72ce5f12877","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦，無人回你d垃圾post架啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好咁啦"},{"pid":"d4677dd891570f58b1640920abacd4e95aefc152","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>i know...</blockquote><br />\nthat feeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c051fe06a5deb61e0616f2546eafad150d3929","tid":108831,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:13:33.000Z","msg":"好怕剪頭髮<br />\n<br />\n每次行入去都會自己俾班mk恥笑緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c3b5aebdeb87a7477a3ab7c3bbf03b1500c728","tid":108831,"uid":59705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:19:45.000Z","msg":"個笑點係邊"},{"pid":"dcc67cf9879056258d4a3e57918ba782512babe1","tid":108831,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好怕剪頭髮<br />\n<br />\n每次行入去都會自己俾班mk恥笑緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />agger"}]}